comments:
I found the study quite interesting, especially for mechanics and aspects, in order to learn the words i have focused on the "h", three of them end with the same letter and therefore i have followed the pattern, that is, the circle was the only one different in that sense, but what guided me the most was with the sound, when i heard it i already knew how it started and ended except for some mistakes.
Regarding patterns, i have noticed that "buvicoh" has been the most common word, that is, the one that has appeared the most times, at least it is my feeling
i have loved the study, above all it is a way of seeing how people are doing in learning language words in a matter of a few minutes, it says a lot about the mentality of each one
